ata element / attribute UID**, not just a static\ncolumn name.\n\nThe earlier PR addressed headers of the form `{stageUid}.{staticColumn}`\n— e.g. `A03MvHHogjR.eventstatus`. It lived in\n`ResponseHelper.normalizeHeaderForGrid`, which runs **after** SQL has\nexecuted: for each requested header, if the suffix matched an existing\ngrid column (`eventstatus`, `eventdate`, `ouname`, …), the grid header\nwas renamed in place to carry the stage prefix the client had asked for.\n\nThat solved the case where the column already existed in the result and\njust needed a stage-scoped name \"reflected\" back.\n\nThis PR fixes a different issue: headers of the form\n`{stageUid}.{dataElementUid}` (e.g. `A03MvHHogjR.a3kGcGDCuk6`) when the\ndata element isn't in any `dimension=`. The column doesn't exist in the\ngrid yet, so renaming it is not possible — it has to be selected.","author":{"name":"Luciano Fiandesio","email":"luciano@fiandesio.com"},"id":"238ab2dff3da22e1cc5691beb831453ea81c9209","tree_id":"9fdc70b9ee3cee8473c9105906b58173c054ace9","timestamp":"2026-04-28T14:39:28Z","committer":{"name":"Luciano Fiandesio","email":"luciano@fiandesio.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/recei